data.description: Welcome to your charming 3-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom with a game room in a desirable neighborhood close to good schools, shopping, dining, major hwys, Randolph AFB & Ft. Sam. This modern gem features elegant gray wood-like ceramic tile, marble vanities, and fresh paint. The spacious living room is bathed in natural light, and the open layout is perfect for entertaining. The backyard is ideal for outdoor enjoyment with an extended covered patio. Make this inviting property your own and start creating lasting memories in a warm, stylish space. The home features a new roof and is ready for you, welcome home!
